Package: airsetup
Title: AI-Assisted R Workflow with QC and Clear Boundaries
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R:
    person("gestimation", "Toolkit", , "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: gestimation Toolkit
Maintainer: gestimation Toolkit <maintainer@example.com>
Description: Lightweight workflow infrastructure for setting up minimal
    AI-assisted R analysis projects. The package creates a controlled AI-visible project
    folder with source, dummy-data, AI-output, R-output, QC, and log areas,
    plus AGENTS.md guidance, QC skill templates, including QC_SKILL_CONTEXT.md,
    QC_SKILL_PLAN.md, QC_SKILL_RESULT.md, QC_SKILL_M11SEMANTIC.md,
    SKILLS_INDEX.md, and a QC_STATUS.md
    tracker. With split = TRUE, it also creates a sibling R execution folder for non-AI-visible
    analysis data. With qc_agent = TRUE, it adds independent QC agent scaffolding and
    Plan gate rules. The package does not implement statistical analysis functions.
